        "name": "SQA: Version-controlled solver with documented release validation",
        "description": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is under formal version control, has a documented release-validation suite covering rotating-machinery benchmarks, and all simulation scripts are archived in a traceable repository. Gradation 2 requires documented SQA process with version control; achieved."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 is a commercially validated solver with documented SQA processes. All simulation input files, boundary condition scripts, and post-processing routines are stored in a version-controlled repository (Git, tag v2.3.1). Release notes and internal benchmark results are on file. Gradation 2 requirement met."
    },
